whereas.text:
Whereas the United States joins together each May to pay
			 tribute to the contributions of generations of Asian Americans and Pacific
			 Islanders who have enriched the Nation’s history;

Whereas the history of Asian Americans and Pacific
			 Islanders in the United States is inextricably tied to the story of the
			 Nation;

Whereas the Asian American and Pacific Islander community
			 is an inherently diverse population, comprised of over 45 distinct ethnicities
			 and over 100 language dialects;
